# Large MoE shapes for grouped GEMM
#
# DeepSeek-V3:        hidden=7168, expert_dim=2048, E=256, top-k=8
#
# M = B×top-k rows distributed across E experts.
# Decode: B=1 token (sparse). Prefill: B=256.

# ── DeepSeek-V3 gate/up projection: K=7168, N=2048 ─────────────────────────
# decode  (B=1 token)
--grouped=0:256::1
8x7168:256x7168x2048nDeepSeek-v3-gate/up-proj-decode-gs128
# prefill (B=256 tokens)
--grouped=0:256::18
2048x7168:256x7168x2048nDeepSeek-v3-gate/up-proj-prefill-gs128

# ── DeepSeek-V3 down projection: K=2048, N=7168 ─────────────────────────────
--grouped=0:256::1
